Yellow Warning For Fog In Belgium - Coastal Zone
alerts.description: Widespread fog with a visibility of maximum 500 m is expected and visibility may locally be less than 200 m. Keep sufficient distance with the car and adjust your speed. Be careful.

alerts.title: Yellow Warning For Ice Snow In Belgium - Coastal Zone
alerts.description: The ground may become slippery due to: 1 to 5 cm fresh snow in 6 hours, or 5 to 10 cm fresh snow in 24 hours, or (very) local black ice, or (very) local frost or ice patches. Be careful.
